title: The Reddit Blackout Got Worse...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at one of the largest Internet blackouts in continuation and discuss how the centralization of some of the most important resources in information have been put behind a wall that only one company can truly control. Reddit needs to come to a conclusion with this blackout and all that takes is reversing some truly greedy decisions. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
